<section class="section" id="problems">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <span class="section__tag">Tanish muammolar</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Bu sizga tanishmi?</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">Kanal egalari har kuni shu muammolarga duch keladi</p>
    </div>

    <div class="problems-grid">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-card__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__content">
          <h3 class="problem-card__pain">Qo'lda invite link berib charchadingizmi?</h3>
          <p class="problem-card__desc">Har bir foydalanuvchiga alohida link yaratish, to'lovni tekshirish, kanalga qo'shish — vaqtingiz ketadi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__solution">
          <div class="solution-tag">Getolog yechimi</div>
          <p>Bot <strong>avtomatik</strong> link yaratadi. To'lov tasdiqlangach — foydalanuvchi darhol link oladi. Siz hech narsa qilmaysiz.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-card__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__content">
          <h3 class="problem-card__pain">Obuna muddati tugaganlarni kuzatib bo'lmayaptimi?</h3>
          <p class="problem-card__desc">Kim qachon kirgan, kimning muddati tugagan — qo'lda nazorat qilish mumkin emas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__solution">
          <div class="solution-tag">Getolog yechimi</div>
          <p>Muddat tugashiga <strong>3 kun va 1 kun</strong> qolganda ogohlantirish. Muddat o'tgach — avtomatik <strong>kanaldan chiqarish</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-card__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__content">
          <h3 class="problem-card__pain">Invite link'ni boshqalarga ulashib ketishyaptimi?</h3>
          <p class="problem-card__desc">Bitta link 10 kishiga tarqalib ketadi. To'lov qilmagan odamlar kanalingizda.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__solution">
          <div class="solution-tag">Getolog yechimi</div>
          <p>Har bir link <strong>faqat 1 marta</strong> ishlaydi (Telegram API cheklovi). Birinchi kirgan oladi — qolganlarga ishlamaydi.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-card__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__content">
          <h3 class="problem-card__pain">To'lovni qabul qilish tizimingiz yo'qmi?</h3>
          <p class="problem-card__desc">Dasturchi yollash qimmat. O'zingiz bot yozishni bilmaysiz. To'lov tizimini ulash murakkab.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card__solution">
          <div class="solution-tag">Getolog yechimi</div>
          <p>Hech narsa yozish kerak emas. <strong>Bot tokenini yuboring</strong> — 2 daqiqada tayyor. Karta to'lovi avtomatik ishlaydi.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problems-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: var(--dark-800);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 233, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(139, 142, 255, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .problem-card__icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .problem-card__pain {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .problem-card__desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--light-400);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-card__solution {
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(230, 233, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .solution-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
    color: var(--success);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .problem-card__solution p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--light-200);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problems-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
